[
  {
    "text": "I've just mentioned this as we, the Beatles,",
    "uid": "8b3ce31cd9555ab1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 8.37,
    "end": 10.81
  },
  {
    "text": "become a theme that I interviewed Paul McCartney",
    "uid": "a5e348f4a19dff6e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 10.81,
    "end": 14.97
  },
  {
    "text": "for the element.",
    "uid": "ac8dff4f7adf1ac2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 14.97,
    "end": 17.33
  },
  {
    "text": "That's it, I shouldn't have just got one.",
    "uid": "aa5ecf848391fdab",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 17.33,
    "end": 26.39
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know, Paul McCartney or Paul, I'm just saying,",
    "uid": "fbb00a990e08cab3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 26.39,
    "end": 34.1
  },
  {
    "text": "went to the Liberal Institute, which is now a lipo.",
    "uid": "43d1bddbb72eade0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 34.1,
    "end": 39.26
  },
  {
    "text": "That wasn't money, man.",
    "uid": "05a100ed8c79b276",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 39.26,
    "end": 40.62
  },
  {
    "text": "I went to the Colleges, the other end of Hope Street.",
    "uid": "b42e3b20c552ddf2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 40.62,
    "end": 43.98
  },
  {
    "text": "And I asked Paul McCartney, I helped a little bit with Leper",
    "uid": "cafd448003e8a5f5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 44.06,
    "end": 49.7
  },
  {
    "text": "in the early days of Mark Featherstone,",
    "uid": "801014b5a9bb1bc0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 49.7,
    "end": 51.42
  },
  {
    "text": "which in the team who got that together,",
    "uid": "55ec60dd895dc4b8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 51.42,
    "end": 53.26
  },
  {
    "text": "it's a fantastic school, by the way.",
    "uid": "d7f8666c177879d0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 53.26,
    "end": 55.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Mark's a wonderful job, and I asked Paul McCartney,",
    "uid": "c723f575c110e866",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 55.5,
    "end": 58.54
  },
  {
    "text": "if he had enjoyed music at school, and he said,",
    "uid": "5ed841188ded2fd6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 58.54,
    "end": 62.86
  },
  {
    "text": "no, he hadn't.",
    "uid": "c3991e24572c6993",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 62.86,
    "end": 64.66
  },
  {
    "text": "I said, your music teacher, you had any talent.",
    "uid": "8cd7c04aa765bfaf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 64.66,
    "end": 67.54
  },
  {
    "text": "He said, no.",
    "uid": "cf78dd302f40f608",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 67.54,
    "end": 69.34
  },
  {
    "text": "He does, doesn't he?",
    "uid": "40ed889517c856ec",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 69.34,
    "end": 71.86
  },
  {
    "text": "One of the other people in the same music program,",
    "uid": "0e6ed18842359b27",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 71.86,
    "end": 73.78
  },
  {
    "text": "at the school, a couple years younger, was George Harrison.",
    "uid": "970f456bb15ea436",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 73.78,
    "end": 78.26
  },
  {
    "text": "And I asked Paul if he thought the teacher thought,",
    "uid": "7c5893322a66e9c8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 78.26,
    "end": 82.38
  },
  {
    "text": "George had any talent, he said, no.",
    "uid": "5a6aaa2b596abe50",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 82.38,
    "end": 85.5
  },
  {
    "text": "So I said, well, look, because part of my argument",
    "uid": "31baed730111b88b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 85.5,
    "end": 88.1
  },
  {
    "text": "is that talent is often buried, you have to be looking for it",
    "uid": "5ac6fb70a94ae108",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 88.1,
    "end": 90.3
  },
  {
    "text": "and create the conditions for it.",
    "uid": "ff7e00ca7775b239",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 90.3,
    "end": 92.34
  },
  {
    "text": "So I said, well, would this be a fair comment",
    "uid": "02793e58880b7881",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 92.34,
    "end": 95.42
  },
  {
    "text": "that there was this one music teacher in Liverpool",
    "uid": "c86133091a36deab",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 95.42,
    "end": 99.02
  },
  {
    "text": "in the late 1950s, who had half the Beatles in his class?",
    "uid": "c891254b605e5bb4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 99.02,
    "end": 103.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And he missed it.",
    "uid": "5e7aa1836f6f4ae3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 103.78,
    "end": 106.62
  },
  {
    "text": "He said, yes, that's right.",
    "uid": "73b8bcf97441bf4d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 106.62,
    "end": 109.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it's a bit of an oversight, isn't it?",
    "uid": "9d24e12c8ed4a401",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 109.86,
    "end": 114.35
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm just saying.",
    "uid": "855c5364e4227130",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 114.35,
    "end": 115.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Elvis Presley, that Elvis mentioned earlier,",
    "uid": "eba66db1836b4250",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 115.87,
    "end": 119.43
  },
  {
    "text": "went to school in Tupolo, Mississippi,",
    "uid": "e5942a2b73980c99",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 119.43,
    "end": 122.27
  },
  {
    "text": "and he wasn't allowed in the Glee Club at school.",
    "uid": "ff58c89155be6848",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 122.27,
    "end": 125.47
  },
  {
    "text": "They said he would ruin their sound.",
    "uid": "6a19270494a22154",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 125.47,
    "end": 128.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, we all know what great heights the Glee Club went on to.",
    "uid": "41d1f692ed387911",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 129.55,
    "end": 131.95
  },
  {
    "text": "One said, man, it's to keep Elvis out of the picture.",
    "uid": "e936474d090634d4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 131.95,
    "end": 137.23
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's the point, isn't it?",
    "uid": "40d5b8af75d455d5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 137.23,
    "end": 138.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Your life is, you created, according to the talent you",
    "uid": "a49d88a3e10b5679",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 138.67,
    "end": 141.19
  },
  {
    "text": "discovered or not.",
    "uid": "d752c4358999cf73",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 141.19,
    "end": 141.95
  },
  {
    "text": "You've mentioned the Dalai Lama.",
    "uid": "5a780466b20a02b8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 141.95,
    "end": 143.91
  },
  {
    "text": "And a few years ago, I hosted a session at the Vancouver Peace",
    "uid": "426de91644f219cf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 143.91,
    "end": 148.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Summit, and he was the guest of honor.",
    "uid": "f64725fcff3e1b52",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 148.27,
    "end": 151.91
  },
  {
    "text": "So we had about 2,000 people in the room.",
    "uid": "4913066c37e304d7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 151.91,
    "end": 153.91
  },
  {
    "text": "It was a session called World Peace through Personal Peace.",
    "uid": "cbf973539011437a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 153.91,
    "end": 158.31
  },
  {
    "text": "So we had about an hour to sort that out.",
    "uid": "0bfdc25733af9aa2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 158.31,
    "end": 162.98
  },
  {
    "text": "We were just killing time for the final 20 minutes, we were on this.",
    "uid": "390c236f37d96328",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 162.98,
    "end": 167.48
  },
  {
    "text": "But I had to introduce the Dalai Lama.",
    "uid": "783ed631fc1779fd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 167.48,
    "end": 170.44
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, her back introduced me.",
    "uid": "284bf1316533f95d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 170.44,
    "end": 171.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it buddhist, as you know, you mentioned the great work, sir.",
    "uid": "1b0a9893a8b6c039",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 171.8,
    "end": 178.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, buddhist believe in reincarnation.",
    "uid": "35c2e4d283cc09ba",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 178.6,
    "end": 180.68
  },
  {
    "text": "So he's the 14th Dalai Lama.",
    "uid": "251ee410ff71a5b6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 180.68,
    "end": 183.08
  },
  {
    "text": "So there's a lot to get in to an introduction.",
    "uid": "6e01ad76ac4bb069",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 183.08,
    "end": 186.12
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're going to be comprehensive about it.",
    "uid": "412f743488b075e7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 186.12,
    "end": 191.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyway, I then realized I didn't have to introduce him.",
    "uid": "4dd1684a4ec71db2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 191.48,
    "end": 194.08
  },
  {
    "text": "As I thought if your name starts with thee, you can relax socially, can't you?",
    "uid": "0c29a8ab7cb26333",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 194.08,
    "end": 199.92
  },
  {
    "text": "At this point.",
    "uid": "363d4f904a67b6a7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 199.92,
    "end": 200.92
  },
  {
    "text": "It doesn't mean.",
    "uid": "93b151ff03d1feae",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 200.92,
    "end": 201.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Excuse me, which Dalai Lama are you?",
    "uid": "7cdf93eaa86c4612",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 201.92,
    "end": 207.08
  },
  {
    "text": "That would be thee.",
    "uid": "87724c8d5c698ec0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 207.08,
    "end": 210.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyway, he said a lot of really great things.",
    "uid": "e1bb126a1ae78314",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 210.17,
    "end": 216.39
  },
  {
    "text": "And as Mike said, a lot of the great truths have been known since the beginning of time.",
    "uid": "9a92f747e6116e0a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 216.39,
    "end": 220.47
  },
  {
    "text": "And they're very simple.",
    "uid": "b0e535f301226f8a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 220.47,
    "end": 222.07
  },
  {
    "text": "But one of the things he was asked a question at some point during this session.",
    "uid": "0fd1079a88efc405",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 222.07,
    "end": 225.83
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're also there, 2,000 people, you know, waiting for the great man to speak.",
    "uid": "0931366bfaa02ccd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 225.83,
    "end": 232.07
  },
  {
    "text": "The right 12, the 10 of us on the panel.",
    "uid": "02f644056480f95b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 232.07,
    "end": 234.35
  },
  {
    "text": "I was, say, facilitating it.",
    "uid": "c4ffd08a695ab83b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 234.35,
    "end": 236.07
  },
  {
    "text": "But he was asked this question.",
    "uid": "9c1de4c02bff82b2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 236.07,
    "end": 237.71
  },
  {
    "text": "You've got a picture.",
    "uid": "2d2026683e3595a8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 237.71,
    "end": 238.71
  },
  {
    "text": "He's sitting cross-legged on a throne.",
    "uid": "43df9fa5fb3fb4b0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 238.71,
    "end": 241.95
  },
  {
    "text": "I did actually ask her for a throne today.",
    "uid": "619eb715895fd3be",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 241.95,
    "end": 243.71
  },
  {
    "text": "But I didn't.",
    "uid": "b8c4aafad99894b1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 243.71,
    "end": 244.71
  },
  {
    "text": "We did get a sofa with a teddy bear.",
    "uid": "a055fb9e0d568e02",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 244.71,
    "end": 247.35
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, so.",
    "uid": "834ce2634dcf4b2d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 247.35,
    "end": 248.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But no, he's sitting cross-legged.",
    "uid": "e80972ee2f7e8089",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 248.59,
    "end": 250.79
  },
  {
    "text": "They're kind of big wooden chair in here.",
    "uid": "7b5be131cc3d0179",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 250.79,
    "end": 252.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And with a baseball cap on.",
    "uid": "b2d3a921f40b712e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 252.51,
    "end": 255.27
  },
  {
    "text": "And he was asked this question.",
    "uid": "0cffecb57d111bf0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 255.27,
    "end": 256.27
  },
  {
    "text": "And he took a deep breath.",
    "uid": "20c9446a99ff66b8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 256.27,
    "end": 259.39
  },
  {
    "text": "And ponder this.",
    "uid": "0a981b9e3d321377",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 259.39,
    "end": 260.39
  },
  {
    "text": "But what about a minute?",
    "uid": "2284f328cf129bbf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 260.39,
    "end": 261.39
  },
  {
    "text": "It's like a long time.",
    "uid": "021582fa7d12e120",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 261.39,
    "end": 263.19
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're all sitting there thinking this is going to be fantastic.",
    "uid": "15c96f0fea527c66",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 263.19,
    "end": 267.11
  },
  {
    "text": "This man has the definite article in his name.",
    "uid": "3fd24e6609ea99a6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 267.11,
    "end": 268.75
  },
  {
    "text": "So it's going to wait till he comes out with this.",
    "uid": "962c98f4637b2fa5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 268.75,
    "end": 271.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And then he let him fall where he took a breath.",
    "uid": "1a0399457ab70239",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 271.59,
    "end": 273.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Here it comes.",
    "uid": "4e3071b532a9fb06",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 273.39,
    "end": 274.75
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, I don't know.",
    "uid": "c1fc72bff06a2245",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 274.75,
    "end": 276.75
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought, what do you mean you don't know?",
    "uid": "5aa690dfd68d55c6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 276.75,
    "end": 281.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, for a dialogue, I'm a, you know, you have the definite article right in your name.",
    "uid": "d2ca3df77bb199bd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 281.14,
    "end": 286.34
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, I'd never thought about that.",
    "uid": "c7c575399114ba8c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 286.34,
    "end": 288.7
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you think?",
    "uid": "522cb0a34b231421",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 288.7,
    "end": 289.7
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you think?",
    "uid": "308e9f9b9041418a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 289.7,
    "end": 290.7
  },
  {
    "text": "You see, I love that.",
    "uid": "ada799eceb0a0009",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 290.7,
    "end": 291.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It's been a theme of the afternoon, isn't it?",
    "uid": "c51b3e2b469c5a1a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 291.7,
    "end": 293.9
  },
  {
    "text": "That knowledge isn't about what you know.",
    "uid": "0529fe7a70ae39af",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 293.9,
    "end": 295.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's about what you don't know.",
    "uid": "a795aa3c54defbd4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 295.5,
    "end": 297.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And being prepared to say, I don't know.",
    "uid": "0cc4070644d25b44",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 297.38,
    "end": 298.78
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to find out.",
    "uid": "e691b132ee1c922a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 298.78,
    "end": 300.02
  },
  {
    "text": "It's run through all the presentations that you're saying about the rest on.",
    "uid": "fb75fbe9f83e44a5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 300.02,
    "end": 302.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "uid": "44873fbfd2ca3c63",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 302.1,
    "end": 303.1
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not over, as long as you're alive and breathing.",
    "uid": "b68ea0f085c118fc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 305.1,
    "end": 307.1
  },
  {
    "text": "And maybe not even then.",
    "uid": "3554e85ec6b4acd8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 307.1,
    "end": 308.98
  },
  {
    "text": "And the great teachers, his, his, one of the world's great teachers, are the people who",
    "uid": "b388dce84f327ff7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 308.98,
    "end": 313.46
  },
  {
    "text": "also learn with their students.",
    "uid": "42e72eb434a9d87e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 313.46,
    "end": 315.1
  },
  {
    "text": "It's one of the big problems of education, we're also supposed to know.",
    "uid": "3dc3fe94736a61ba",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 315.66,
    "end": 317.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And you've got it wrong, you fail.",
    "uid": "28300c9edcd863b8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 317.46,
    "end": 319.06
  },
  {
    "text": "And actually all the great questions aren't terribly noble, even at the heart of science.",
    "uid": "86a0c409a7fdd9d6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 319.06,
    "end": 323.22
  },
  {
    "text": "The other thing you said, by the way, is, instead of things,",
    "uid": "0c597218275d0043",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 323.22,
    "end": 325.82
  },
  {
    "text": "but he said that, to be born at all, is a miracle.",
    "uid": "feea6e532b504dc6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 325.82,
    "end": 330.62
  },
  {
    "text": "So what are you going to do with your life?",
    "uid": "a3916b3f0fdede4d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 330.62,
    "end": 333.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And this really resonated with me.",
    "uid": "20e0f04c10b05513",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 333.02,
    "end": 334.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Sam from Liverpool.",
    "uid": "23a9a3654f3848bb",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 334.1,
    "end": 334.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm one of seven kids.",
    "uid": "db01ddffc82e40d5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 334.94,
    "end": 336.14
  },
  {
    "text": "And my brother John, who's sitting right there, behind the drum.",
    "uid": "c8b95631eb4249f9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 336.14,
    "end": 340.1
  },
  {
    "text": "My brother John.",
    "uid": "504a61649da49222",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 340.1,
    "end": 341.78
  },
  {
    "text": "I had my arm round in most after, and I just want to explain what was going on there.",
    "uid": "fb23e93438656acc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 341.78,
    "end": 344.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's so easily misinterpreted.",
    "uid": "cb7a418f5da5319b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 344.74,
    "end": 352.14
  },
  {
    "text": "But I don't mind if it is, but I know that's John.",
    "uid": "cafd18b684a45527",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 352.14,
    "end": 355.62
  },
  {
    "text": "John has been doing our family tree.",
    "uid": "233763570fab02ce",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 355.62,
    "end": 359.9
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not much of a tree, it's like a small shrub, isn't it, really?",
    "uid": "9e38c0fa38d70e9d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 359.9,
    "end": 363.86
  },
  {
    "text": "With a fungus infection in the roots of what we can make out.",
    "uid": "270549ca5ad365eb",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 363.86,
    "end": 367.3
  },
  {
    "text": "But he discovered that seven of our eight great grandparents were all born in Liverpool",
    "uid": "334630478a06856e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 367.3,
    "end": 373.5
  },
  {
    "text": "in the 19th century, within two miles of each other.",
    "uid": "49f0cd00bea65dfe",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 373.5,
    "end": 377.02
  },
  {
    "text": "That's how they met.",
    "uid": "d7fa9e573dfb7d08",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 377.02,
    "end": 378.38
  },
  {
    "text": "They ran into each other.",
    "uid": "9bd5dcaef3302684",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 378.38,
    "end": 380.1
  },
  {
    "text": "That's how people used to meet.",
    "uid": "4cb35a65eb9ab312",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 380.1,
    "end": 381.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Life was very local.",
    "uid": "0e385375c1f5df75",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 381.3,
    "end": 382.98
  },
  {
    "text": "People didn't travel great distances like you all do.",
    "uid": "2ae8d453b3043651",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 382.98,
    "end": 384.94
  },
  {
    "text": "People just went to work and came home.",
    "uid": "d69d9b809e2bfcba",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 384.94,
    "end": 386.78
  },
  {
    "text": "It was as far as they could walk, and they would come back again.",
    "uid": "1bb7b1a295c6fa1d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 386.78,
    "end": 390.5
  },
  {
    "text": "So that's how they met.",
    "uid": "61807468136cec3a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 390.5,
    "end": 391.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you might say, no, that's not the case.",
    "uid": "64e2caf76f1790bb",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 391.5,
    "end": 393.06
  },
  {
    "text": "You're missing the point.",
    "uid": "49794a72ed7d390b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 393.06,
    "end": 394.1
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a cosmic theme here that you've misunderstood.",
    "uid": "66928a24d09d655a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 394.1,
    "end": 397.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The cosmos erines things, that these eight soulmates converge at the same point",
    "uid": "cbbc691eeb4bd088",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 397.46,
    "end": 402.7
  },
  {
    "text": "at the space time continuum that they should meet and procreate and continue the process.",
    "uid": "962a150b9f80c6db",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 402.7,
    "end": 406.62
  },
  {
    "text": "That has led to the miracle that it is me.",
    "uid": "a218f7f6b211a57a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 406.62,
    "end": 410.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a way of thinking about, I don't think so.",
    "uid": "4e62d920e63bc163",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 410.7,
    "end": 414.98
  },
  {
    "text": "I just think they had lower standards then, frankly.",
    "uid": "32afd89f318eb42f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 414.98,
    "end": 417.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I think people ran into each other in the street and thought you will do.",
    "uid": "d6b1d4fdf38f65cb",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 417.1,
    "end": 420.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I could spend my life with you.",
    "uid": "872c196a3bb2ff99",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 420.94,
    "end": 426.36
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd been constantly embarrassed, this will be fine.",
    "uid": "2307c5991bda4b0b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 426.36,
    "end": 428.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Because they didn't know Angelina Jolie was in prospect, or brand-purt.",
    "uid": "48449fe76d03c571",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 428.6,
    "end": 432.44
  },
  {
    "text": "They didn't have TMZ or people magazine.",
    "uid": "4b008af5ba17f88c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 432.44,
    "end": 434.52
  },
  {
    "text": "It was just like the people around.",
    "uid": "d3218b66b98fd588",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 434.52,
    "end": 436.72
  },
  {
    "text": "But here's the point you see.",
    "uid": "851d6517ba80f70e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 436.72,
    "end": 438.52
  },
  {
    "text": "They went on and had kids and eventually my hard-ground parents were born and then our parents",
    "uid": "f52ef74b7dc88331",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 438.52,
    "end": 443.68
  },
  {
    "text": "50 odd years later, and there was that night in the pub.",
    "uid": "46bd64f214c2b930",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 445.68,
    "end": 451.16
  },
  {
    "text": "And here we are, it's a miracle, father.",
    "uid": "ddb0576687a274ac",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 451.16,
    "end": 454.12
  },
  {
    "text": "But the thing is, I tell you about that, because if you think of the chances of you being born",
    "uid": "64656ff95f7165bd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 454.12,
    "end": 459.24
  },
  {
    "text": "at all, they're pretty remote, very statistically.",
    "uid": "84c119f4d73a325c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 459.24,
    "end": 462.32
  },
  {
    "text": "All the people are happy to meet in what circumstance.",
    "uid": "f713cab761d8716a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 462.32,
    "end": 464.48
  },
  {
    "text": "I think how you met your partner, if you have one.",
    "uid": "7d87c3811ca02dd7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 464.48,
    "end": 466.56
  },
  {
    "text": "That's a pretty remote.",
    "uid": "5d7b1b7a8001ea96",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 466.56,
    "end": 467.84
  },
  {
    "text": "The thing that things you do and how that came about, your whole life is composed by the choices",
    "uid": "22568df8ad37ac89",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 467.84,
    "end": 471.84
  },
  {
    "text": "The turnings you move towards, the ones you turn away from, the chance you're prepared to risk,",
    "uid": "79063709724d6ab2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 472.84,
    "end": 477.4
  },
  {
    "text": "the way you deal with your fear or you don't.",
    "uid": "68fad85eba2e467e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 477.4,
    "end": 479.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And in the process, you create a life of some sort.",
    "uid": "00753df15a6ab05f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 479.64,
    "end": 482.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's a miracle.",
    "uid": "515c758a2b7b3823",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 482.64,
    "end": 483.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And it amazed me how little people settle for very often.",
    "uid": "4cdc4a2fa0733bfc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 483.64,
    "end": 486.44
  },
  {
    "text": "They go through the whole of the lives in a state of anxiety, thinking, well, if a try it",
    "uid": "b9023ed494392013",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 486.44,
    "end": 489.8
  },
  {
    "text": "it won't work.",
    "uid": "93e685ef079c33ab",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 489.8,
    "end": 491.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone who ever achieved anything in their lives was prepared to be wrong and make a mistake",
    "uid": "7fb88b2a8fd20df1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 491.92,
    "end": 495.36
  },
  {
    "text": "in trying it.",
    "uid": "94ead200817dc47f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 495.36,
    "end": 496.84
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's how culture progresses, how our lives progress, it's how you build a legacy and have a life",
    "uid": "12e169384108e24b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 496.84,
    "end": 501.48
  },
  {
    "text": "in the process.",
    "uid": "db01811c04d39b67",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 501.48,
    "end": 502.84
  },
  {
    "text": "And everyone makes their own choice about that sort of thing.",
    "uid": "46c215573e3e5d55",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 502.84,
    "end": 505.76
  },
  {
    "text": "And I just feel that's been one of the great features of this afternoon.",
    "uid": "f8113f06e708d543",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 505.76,
    "end": 509.6
  },
  {
    "text": "And this morning I'm sure I wasn't able to be here.",
    "uid": "f635680d427a1544",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 509.6,
    "end": 512.32
  },
  {
    "text": "We've had lots of examples of people who created very different sorts of lives, no effect",
    "uid": "1dd0f1f55d7d17e8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 512.32,
    "end": 515.48
  },
  {
    "text": "in people very differently.",
    "uid": "b7185d1de69060db",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 515.48,
    "end": 517.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's in the way that we do that, that we create a culture.",
    "uid": "a93129d1e929b28f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 517.2,
    "end": 519.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And if we get the culture right, then we create a life that we can",
    "uid": "978dfcbc50587f22",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 519.2,
    "end": 521.4
  },
  {
    "text": "all live, commonly.",
    "uid": "c401a1faf26823e6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 521.4,
    "end": 523.24
  },
  {
    "text": "And my final thought in all this is, that's the difference between human beings, the rest",
    "uid": "b710ac98e3e590df",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 523.24,
    "end": 526.76
  },
  {
    "text": "of life on earth.",
    "uid": "fd5e6cfbaa8a0e78",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 526.76,
    "end": 527.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, we are jeopardizing the rest of life on earth and the way that we're behaving.",
    "uid": "bddaa6ceb5ded665",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 527.76,
    "end": 531.2
  },
  {
    "text": "But the interesting thing is that human culture is always progressing through this power",
    "uid": "abbdfc8e479a0ec9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 531.2,
    "end": 535.52
  },
  {
    "text": "of imagination and creativity.",
    "uid": "aa87640cfe6cf0b6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 535.52,
    "end": 537.16
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a big difference, isn't it, between us, the rest of life on earth, although we're",
    "uid": "5edf2313036c403a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 537.16,
    "end": 539.72
  },
  {
    "text": "intimately connected to it and we keep forgetting it?",
    "uid": "0219eca7d9edc52f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 539.72,
    "end": 542.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, if you've got a dog, you know, your dog probably has all kinds of feelings.",
    "uid": "64f44593664a4068",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 542.36,
    "end": 547.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And may have some kind of imagination.",
    "uid": "71ebf30a6b49652b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 547.64,
    "end": 549.6
  },
  {
    "text": "But it doesn't manifest, it doesn't, in quite the same way.",
    "uid": "d4580b3d2af1979c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 549.6,
    "end": 552.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't see your dog strung out the window, depressed, reading Camo.",
    "uid": "5b9611ec04384088",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 552.56,
    "end": 555.84
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a business, they say, you want to come for a walk and another.",
    "uid": "1591f84ee4653f62",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 555.84,
    "end": 558.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you go, I'm not in the mood, you go, you go.",
    "uid": "a53fb003d4adbc56",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 558.84,
    "end": 570.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Because we live in a virtual world, we live in the world of ideas, we live in a world of thoughts",
    "uid": "814da82e97f7c582",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 570.14,
    "end": 573.74
  },
  {
    "text": "and feelings and theories and possibilities.",
    "uid": "41529ac34dbde53d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 573.74,
    "end": 575.78
  },
  {
    "text": "And, you know, it's the old maxim that nothing, you know, is so powerful as an idea",
    "uid": "8f8bd0cb361fa9b7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 575.78,
    "end": 579.9
  },
  {
    "text": "whose time has come.",
    "uid": "0e4b86c316f77b8a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 579.9,
    "end": 580.9
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, nothing is so influential as a life well-lived.",
    "uid": "705b2bdc259889d9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 580.9,
    "end": 584.58
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's really, I think, what today's been about and I wanted on your behalf to thank",
    "uid": "4efcc3bf2b8a59a8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 584.58,
    "end": 589.66
  },
  {
    "text": "all the speakers this afternoon, Mike for a wonderful round off.",
    "uid": "f647b0bd5271d32f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 589.66,
    "end": 593.26
  },
  {
    "text": "And especially her, from bringing all this together.",
    "uid": "54564cd53d5354b6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 593.26,
    "end": 595.82
  },
  {
    "text": "So please welcome her, Camo.",
    "uid": "b38408b64838778b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 595.82,
    "end": 597.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for the round applause for the Sir Ken Robinson, for a guest hosting this final session.",
    "uid": "cff21c28c0eb1cbe",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 597.34,
    "end": 616.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And of course I've got to repeat my thanks to all the speakers all day, which have been amazing.",
    "uid": "041af3637cb33b61",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 616.38,
    "end": 635.32
  },
  {
    "text": "I should also add, of course, our own staff, the staff at the every man who have been",
    "uid": "fbc993f123dc9423",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 635.32,
    "end": 640.44
  },
  {
    "text": "robbed and has crewed up there, I've been busy making sure all the stuff behind us is",
    "uid": "2df4c5f6e8490c46",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 640.44,
    "end": 643.68
  },
  {
    "text": "working well and things like microphones and such.",
    "uid": "e337470ca49503be",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 643.68,
    "end": 646.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Like, is Marie-Ren, Marie-Berns, who is a producer of this year's TEDx?",
    "uid": "89882b60fb43299a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - Life_is_your_talents_discovered_Sir_Ken_Robinson_TEDxLiverpool",
    "start": 646.36,
    "end": 650.4
  }
]